# Running Tests

## Run all tests:

pnpm run test

## Run a specific test file:

pnpm run test <testFilePath>

## Example:

pnpm run test ./src/converter/mermaid-sanitizer.test.ts

# Rules

- Do not use `cd`
- Commands must be run from the project root
- Never change directories before running tests
